    <string name="change_log"><![CDATA[
        <section>
            <header><h2>Version 1.2.1</h2></header>
            <p>Small bugfix release.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Fixed a crash when adding authors from unknown urls.</li>
                <li>Fixed a crash when importing authors from unknown urls.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <header><h2>Version 1.2.0</h2></header>
            <ul>
                <li>Added import and export support. txt and xml formats are supported.</li>
                <li>Added google back-up. Now the content is synchronized between your devices. Not guaranteed, "backup" and "restore" must be enabled in device settings.</li>
                <li>Added possibility to add authors from budclub.ru</li>
                <li>Support for interactive download folder choosing.</li>
                <li>Fixed author removal. Now all related publications are removed as well.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <header><h2>Version 1.1.2</h2></header>
            <p>Small bugfix release.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Multiple issue fixes. Specifically for Motorola and Asus Transformer as well as an issues specific to GT-I8150 only.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <header><h2>Version 1.1.1</h2></header>
            <ul>
                <li>Added option of configuring download directory for publications. When files are saved to a custom filder - they have a meaningfull name</li>
                <li>Fixed several issues due to bad connection and samlib being unavailable.</li>
                <li>Added option of clearing saved publications. (Clears only the default directory)</li>
                <li>Added optional publication images when available</li>
            </ul>
        </section>


        <section>
            <header><h2>Version 1.1.0</h2></header>
            <p>Warning: all your publications will be marked as new after the update.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Added permission "Storage" for saving publications</li>
                <li>On long press, publication is downloaded for viewing in apps like CoolReader or AIReader. "Open in browser" functionality was removed and will be added back later.</li>
                <li>Publication description is save in html format now with working links</li>
                <li>Fixed several issues related to poor connection</li>
                <li>Added author multiselection for devices with Android &lt; 3.0</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    ]]></string>

